'''Bjarni Corfitzen''' is an [[Main/en/OpenTTD]] [[Main/en/Developers|developer]] who maintained the MacOS X port of OpenTTD.

Bjarni also writes and has written and maintains many vehicle related features, including Clone Vehicles and [[Main/en/Replace vehicles#Autoreplace]], allowing for better management of a large [[Main/en/Transport Company|transport company's]] vehicles.